Interface Form

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Form.Arc2D, Form.CubicCurve2D, Form.Ellipse2D, Form.Line2D, Form.Path2D, Form.Rectangle2D

    public interface Form
    The interface and the classes that implement it used by all shapes in renderer.shape.javafx for create and display a javafx.scene.shape.Shape in a Canvas.
